## Next Steps

* **`draft-ietf-tcpm-tcp-ghost-acks`**: Working Group members are urged to review the document and provide feedback during the ongoing WGLC.
* **`draft-ietf-tcpm-ack-rate-request`**: The chairs will evaluate the readiness of the document for WGLC on the mailing list.
* **TCP Extended Options / TCP EDO**: The working group will continue discussions on the mailing list regarding how to proceed with extending the TCP option space, evaluating EDO vs. the Seg-U proposal.
* **TCP Packet Trimming**: The authors will refine the proposal based on feedback regarding in-band DSCP negotiation and out-of-domain leakage, and continue the discussion on the mailing list.